l production and is in the exploration stage during the month of december in  shehzad inc acquired  of silvercorp metals over a period of a week shehzad inc manages the equities and investing on behalf of silvercorp yangtze mining ltd holds a  interest in anhui yangtze mining co ltd the chinese company holding silver lead and zinc exploration permits on the gaocheng project and shimentou project in the guangdong province in june  silvercorp metals acquired yangtze gold ltd contents  history  fraud  references  external links historyedit the company started out as a minor explorer trading on the tsx venture exchange from november  to october  was incorporated under the british columbia company act in  at first it was known as spokane resources ltd until  when it was renamed skn resources ltd in  the same year it graduated from the tsx venture exchange to the larger toronto exchange it adopted its current name in  silvercorp donated rmb million towards the construction of a youth center in luoning county henan province china fraudedit in  a canadiannationalized chinese kun huang investigated silvercorp for his employer eosfunds and found strong differences between their reports filed in china and in canada further investigation lead to further proofs for fraud eg regarding the reported amount of silver produced as reaction of detecting the fraud mr huang was convicted and imprisoned in china for his investigation after release mr huang pressed charges against silvercorp in canada for false imprisonment referencesedit  silvercorp donates rmb million yuan towards the construction of a youth center   description of the investigation of kun huang against silvercorp   canadian stock researcher sues silvercorp over ‘false imprisonment’ in china  external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlesilvercorpmetalsoldid categories companies listed on the toronto stock exchangecompanies listed on the new york stock exchangemining companies of ca