nd a better understanding of internal and external factors which could impact the industry increase businesssales activities by understanding your competitors’ businesses better recognize potential partnerships and supplierskey highlightssilvercorp metals inc silvercorp is a mining exploration company it carries out acquisition exploration development and mining of precious and base metal mineral properties the company mines metals such as gold silver lead zinc and sulphur in china it operates four silverleadzinc mines which include ying mine hpg mine tlp mine and lm mine silvercorp also operates the byp goldleadzinc project in hunan province and gc silverleadzinc project in guangdong province and the xhp silvergoldleadzinc mines in zhengzhou henan province the company sells its products to local smelters and companies which involves in the mineral products trading business silvercorp is headquartered in vancouver british columbia canada show less read more note product cover images may vary from those shown  of  login to access executive summary printer friendly printable pdf brochure send to a friend  silvercorp metals inc  business analysis silvercorp metals inc  company overview silvercorp metals inc  business description silvercorp metals inc  major products and services silvercorp metals inc  analysis of key performance indicators silvercorp metals inc  five year snapshot overview of financial and operational performance indicators silvercorp metals inc  key financial performance indicators silvercorp metals inc  revenue and operating profit silvercorp metals inc  asset and liabilities silvercorp metals inc  operational efficiency silvercorp metals inc  solvency silvercorp metals inc  valuation silvercorp metals inc  key competitors silvercorp metals inc  mergers  acquisitions and partnerships silvercorp metals inc  ma and partnerships strategy silvercorp metals inc  recent developments silvercorp metals inc  swot analysis silvercorp metals inc  swot analysis 